  <p></center><font size='2' color="maroon">
   Welcome to Guimaras Disaster Assessment System! This is a computer software that automatically computes the impact of disaster in Guimaras. This system is integrated with decision support that aids in the computations and identifications of needs of the victims of natural disasters, for a fair, precise and timely distribution of services.
  </p><br>
